WEBVTT

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.900
Play these ones in a row

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:56.040
And nobody can stop you

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:56.659
Right

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:57.519
Shunzi

00:01:57.799 --> 00:01:58.480
Yusheng

00:01:59.319 --> 00:02:00.219
That's not fair

00:02:00.620 --> 00:02:02.480
You just saw my cards

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.980
Then went to help him

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:05.400
This is cards

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:06.159
Not chess

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:07.340
It's all exposed now

00:02:07.340 --> 00:02:08.159
Sorry

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:09.340
Professor Fan, too

00:02:09.340 --> 00:02:10.379
Sorry about that, Boss Li

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.460
I'll help you check your cards

00:02:11.460 --> 00:02:12.500
We won't let him look

00:02:12.500 --> 00:02:12.939
Okay

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.259
Help me take a look

00:02:14.819 --> 00:02:15.680
How should I play this?

00:02:15.979 --> 00:02:16.439
This one

00:02:18.460 --> 00:02:18.979
Okay

00:02:20.379 --> 00:02:21.680
Hello? Mommy

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:27.199
Any new progress?

00:02:32.740 --> 00:02:33.539
No

00:02:33.639 --> 00:02:35.699
I haven't thought it through yet

00:02:35.780 --> 00:02:36.340
You and Dad

00:02:36.340 --> 00:02:37.919
Can't decide for me again

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:41.379
Alright

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:43.379
Can we talk about this later?

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.219
I'm busy right now

00:02:47.259 --> 00:02:47.680
Okay

00:02:47.819 --> 00:02:48.580
Bye-bye, Mommy

00:02:57.159 --> 00:02:57.860
Yingzi

00:02:58.680 --> 00:02:59.759
That phone call of yours

00:03:00.219 --> 00:03:01.460
Look at this great hand

00:03:01.460 --> 00:03:02.520
It's completely ruined

00:03:02.580 --> 00:03:03.439
Sorry, Boss Li

00:03:03.439 --> 00:03:04.159
Coming

00:03:07.580 --> 00:03:08.379
Is it about

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:10.960
your family discussing you going abroad for grad school?

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:12.699
It's hardly a discussion.

00:03:12.979 --> 00:03:13.919
It's an order.

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:15.039
So you...

00:03:15.719 --> 00:03:16.840
have to leave right after graduation?

00:03:18.819 --> 00:03:20.159
That's what my dad wants.

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:22.120
But what do *you* want?

00:03:22.479 --> 00:03:22.919
Me?

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:25.719
I don't really have a plan.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.439
Actually,

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:31.699
our domestic education standards aren't low.

00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:33.759
We have so many professors

00:03:33.979 --> 00:03:34.560
and doctoral supervisors.

00:03:35.379 --> 00:03:37.680
You don't have to go abroad to further your studies.

00:03:37.919 --> 00:03:39.120
Don't you agree, Professor Fan?

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:41.919
I actually think

00:03:41.979 --> 00:03:43.620
going out to broaden your horizons

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:44.680
is a good thing.

00:03:44.939 --> 00:03:45.139
I mean,

00:03:45.139 --> 00:03:46.479
read ten thousand books, travel ten thousand miles.

00:03:46.479 --> 00:03:46.879
Right?

00:03:47.819 --> 00:03:48.719
I think

00:03:48.939 --> 00:03:50.139
going abroad is useless.

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:53.979
Grandpa Boss Li's opinion is important too.

00:03:54.159 --> 00:03:54.759
Come on,

00:03:55.020 --> 00:03:56.319
tell us all about it.

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:57.840
Especially for Yingzi.

00:03:59.900 --> 00:04:01.340
Since you've achieved academic success,

00:04:02.039 --> 00:04:03.780
you should, as soon as possible,

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:04.680
devote yourself to

00:04:04.719 --> 00:04:07.000
the current modernization efforts.

00:04:07.860 --> 00:04:09.259
Use the knowledge you've learned

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:11.419
for the country,

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:12.500
for society,

00:04:12.620 --> 00:04:13.560
and for the people,

00:04:13.740 --> 00:04:15.039
to make more contributions.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.779
I think going abroad to learn more skills

00:04:18.860 --> 00:04:20.980
and then returning to serve the country isn't too late.

00:04:22.300 --> 00:04:24.540
I don't think Yingzi should go.

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:26.139
It's so chaotic out there.

00:04:26.220 --> 00:04:27.839
What don't we have here?

00:04:27.959 --> 00:04:29.139
Why do you have to go out

00:04:29.139 --> 00:04:30.980
and get caught in a school shooting?

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:33.240
I agree with Xiao Cai's analysis.

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:36.259
Going abroad is no small matter.

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:39.180
It could change your entire life.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:41.379
You know me,

00:04:41.399 --> 00:04:42.959
I've never been very decisive.

00:04:43.259 --> 00:04:44.680
After listening to all your advice,

00:04:45.860 --> 00:04:47.420
I'm even less sure of what to do.

00:04:48.939 --> 00:04:49.660
Yingzi,

00:04:49.939 --> 00:04:51.500
this is a major life decision.

00:04:52.220 --> 00:04:53.759
You must make the decision yourself

00:04:53.959 --> 00:04:55.279
so you won't regret it later.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:57.699
When I was your age,

00:04:57.920 --> 00:05:00.019
just because I took one wrong step,

00:05:00.459 --> 00:05:01.279
I've regretted it my whole life.

00:05:01.399 --> 00:05:02.540
Really?

00:05:03.420 --> 00:05:04.019
Absolutely.

00:05:04.259 --> 00:05:04.939
Otherwise,

00:05:05.019 --> 00:05:06.579
why would I end up like this?

00:05:06.779 --> 00:05:07.459
Hanging out with you...

00:05:07.699 --> 00:05:08.100
No,

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:09.459
hanging out with Old Li.

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.240
What's wrong with playing cards with me?

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.259
That's your good fortune.

00:05:15.939 --> 00:05:17.439
It's just one wrong step.

00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:19.800
Like no one else has ever made a mistake.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:22.459
You even argue about this?

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:23.939
I'm not arguing.

00:05:24.100 --> 00:05:25.819
I really did make a mistake.

00:05:26.740 --> 00:05:27.639
But so what?

00:05:28.079 --> 00:05:29.439
I've regretted it for half my life.

00:05:31.860 --> 00:05:33.079
We've all been there.

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:34.579
You too?

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:35.579
Of course.

00:05:36.660 --> 00:05:37.879
Back then, Director Zhang...

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:40.279
the one who won the Golden Cat Award...

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:41.199
for that movie.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:43.040
He came to me first.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:45.379
He wanted me to play Cixi.

00:05:46.839 --> 00:05:48.860
Playing Cixi at such a young age.

00:05:49.139 --> 00:05:50.319
The young Cixi.

00:05:51.319 --> 00:05:52.519
Director Zhang had his eye on me.

00:05:53.079 --> 00:05:55.860
If I had done that movie back then,

00:05:56.180 --> 00:05:58.620
I'd be a multi-award-winning actress now.

00:06:01.300 --> 00:06:02.920
But Director Zhang...

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:04.259
The casting couch? You refused?

00:06:04.360 --> 00:06:04.860
Good for you.

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.819
What are you thinking?

00:06:08.279 --> 00:06:09.860
It's just that Director Zhang and I

00:06:10.980 --> 00:06:12.800
didn't get along at all.

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:13.800
Let's not talk about it.

00:06:13.959 --> 00:06:14.519
Let's play cards.

00:06:15.959 --> 00:06:17.500
Speaking of wrong steps,

00:06:18.019 --> 00:06:18.579
actually,

00:06:18.819 --> 00:06:19.920
I made a mistake too.

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:23.980
Back then, a really handsome guy liked me.

00:06:26.740 --> 00:06:28.620
I let that opportunity slip away.

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:30.459
Now,

00:06:30.660 --> 00:06:32.660
he's already a Chief Engineer.

00:06:33.279 --> 00:06:35.600
If I hadn't missed that chance back then,

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:36.540
and married him,

00:06:37.060 --> 00:06:39.480
I wouldn't have ended up marrying into the Chen family,

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.939
and being a widow all my life.

00:06:42.060 --> 00:06:42.920
Oh, life...

00:06:43.620 --> 00:06:43.899
Sei-

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.560
Seizing opportunities is too important.

00:06:46.839 --> 00:06:47.699
Old Li, it's your turn.

00:06:50.259 --> 00:06:50.500
It's your turn.

00:06:50.500 --> 00:06:51.220
Play a card.

00:07:05.139 --> 00:07:05.779
Stop looking.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:07.699
Rush over there and confess.

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:08.360
You...

00:07:09.079 --> 00:07:10.500
You are my... right?

00:07:10.779 --> 00:07:11.759
Grandpa?

00:07:11.779 --> 00:07:12.620
Nonsense.

00:07:12.740 --> 00:07:13.660
Am I that old?

00:07:15.420 --> 00:07:16.540
Actually, pretty close.

00:07:17.420 --> 00:07:18.720
I am you.

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:21.120
You, forty years from now.

00:07:21.939 --> 00:07:22.620
I know.

00:07:22.819 --> 00:07:23.860
You came today...

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:25.199
to confess your love to Jing Xian.

00:07:25.519 --> 00:07:26.379
I came specifically to help you.

00:07:26.699 --> 00:07:27.399
Alright then.

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:30.079
Help me chase that Guo Lixin away right now.

00:07:30.259 --> 00:07:31.120
Guo Lixin?

00:07:31.180 --> 00:07:33.319
He's on the school team for Throwing Events.

00:07:34.199 --> 00:07:35.439
Even you couldn't beat him.

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:38.100
I'm an old man over sixty; fight him?

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:40.379
Then how can you help me?

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:43.040
I... am here to remind you.

00:07:43.379 --> 00:07:44.319
This is the critical moment...

00:07:44.439 --> 00:07:45.980
that decides your whole life.

00:07:46.060 --> 00:07:47.060
You must seize it.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.540
Confess loudly!

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:50.660
Actually, Jing Xian...

00:07:50.860 --> 00:07:52.180
likes you.

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:53.139
Me?

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:54.180
Us.

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:55.360
Really?

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:56.860
She likes...

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:58.019
you.

00:07:58.579 --> 00:07:59.240
Us.

00:08:01.819 --> 00:08:03.560
But if I just go up and confess like this,

00:08:04.500 --> 00:08:06.220
what if she rejects me?

00:08:06.819 --> 00:08:08.639
What if Guo Lixin beats me up?

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:09.339
Don't be afraid.

00:08:09.740 --> 00:08:11.500
Guo Lixin didn't beat me up later on.

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:14.240
He has his weakness.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:16.199
Okay.

00:08:17.579 --> 00:08:18.540
Then I'll...

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:22.600
I'm still a bit...

00:08:22.699 --> 00:08:23.279
What's wrong?

00:08:24.699 --> 00:08:26.439
Since you are me,

00:08:26.779 --> 00:08:28.100
you should know clearly.

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:30.279
That's just our personality.

00:08:30.779 --> 00:08:31.899
Of course I know.

00:08:31.899 --> 00:08:32.600
Cowardly.

00:08:32.659 --> 00:08:33.600
Socially anxious.

00:08:33.659 --> 00:08:34.360
A wimp.

00:08:34.620 --> 00:08:36.580
That's why I came to encourage you!

00:08:36.820 --> 00:08:38.000
Seize this opportunity.

00:08:38.139 --> 00:08:38.820
Otherwise,

00:08:39.179 --> 00:08:40.080
in the future, we...

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:41.639
will have no children,

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:43.019
be all alone,

00:08:43.179 --> 00:08:44.679
and die of old age in a nursing home,

00:08:44.940 --> 00:08:46.480
playing cards with a bunch of old people.

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:47.340
Do you understand?

00:08:47.860 --> 00:08:49.580
Is this your way of encouraging me?

00:08:50.159 --> 00:08:52.039
This is practically intimidation!

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:53.460
Besides,

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.399
we're such a catch,

00:08:55.639 --> 00:08:57.639
how could we end up all alone?

00:08:57.919 --> 00:08:58.720
Cut the crap.

00:08:59.100 --> 00:08:59.580
Go!

00:09:01.179 --> 00:09:02.580
Watch where you're going!

00:09:04.659 --> 00:09:05.460
Dacheng?

00:09:07.940 --> 00:09:08.559
Xiao Fan?

00:09:09.299 --> 00:09:10.279
What are you doing here?

00:09:10.419 --> 00:09:11.179
I...

00:09:11.559 --> 00:09:12.159
Nothing.

00:09:17.919 --> 00:09:18.639
Brother Guo

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:21.340
I just came to take a look

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:23.980
Are you dating Jing Xian?

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:24.840
That's right

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:25.659
Why?

00:09:25.899 --> 00:09:27.299
Do I need your permission?

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.100
Da Cheng

00:09:28.379 --> 00:09:29.480
Speak if you have something to say

00:09:30.980 --> 00:09:31.740
I...

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:33.200
I...

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.240
Old Fan

00:09:36.620 --> 00:09:37.940
What should I do?

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.980
Why are you such a coward?

00:09:41.519 --> 00:09:42.340
We...

00:09:43.220 --> 00:09:44.539
Is it "we" who are cowardly?

00:09:44.600 --> 00:09:45.500
It's just you

00:09:45.500 --> 00:09:45.840
I...

00:09:46.220 --> 00:09:46.980
Back then

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:50.080
If I had known Jing Xian liked me deep down

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.899
I definitely would have taken that step

00:09:52.379 --> 00:09:52.840
I...

00:09:54.059 --> 00:09:54.519
He...

00:09:55.059 --> 00:09:55.460
I...

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:58.259
I really can't take that step

00:09:58.639 --> 00:09:59.279
You...

00:09:59.620 --> 00:10:00.220
Come here

00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:01.100
I'll tell you

00:10:01.179 --> 00:10:02.879
some key information

00:10:11.679 --> 00:10:12.519
Really?

00:10:14.259 --> 00:10:14.740
Okay

00:10:15.460 --> 00:10:16.039
Don't worry

00:10:16.379 --> 00:10:18.580
I'm going to take this crucial step in life

00:10:25.139 --> 00:10:26.679
I like Jing Xian

00:10:26.899 --> 00:10:28.100
And she likes me too

00:10:28.679 --> 00:10:30.440
Please stay away from her from now on

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:33.879
You'll have to get past me first

00:10:34.100 --> 00:10:34.700
What?

00:10:35.279 --> 00:10:36.480
Want to compete?

00:10:37.820 --> 00:10:38.460
Compete in what?

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:40.940
Long-distance running or swimming?

00:10:41.759 --> 00:10:43.820
Aren't you afraid your heart disease will act up?

00:10:46.940 --> 00:10:48.340
You have heart disease?

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:50.879
This disease...

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:51.980
It's hereditary, right?

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:53.659
I...

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:54.519
I don't...

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:56.460
I didn't tell anyone

00:10:57.399 --> 00:10:58.440
I don't have heart disease

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.980
Wait, how do you know?

00:11:01.460 --> 00:11:03.019
Rheumatic myocarditis

00:11:03.740 --> 00:11:05.500
And you're about to have an attack

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:07.679
You're talking nonsense

00:11:09.299 --> 00:11:10.580
I advise you

00:11:11.080 --> 00:11:13.299
to hurry and get your Bureau Chief dad

00:11:13.820 --> 00:11:15.120
to pull some strings for you

00:11:15.220 --> 00:11:16.720
and find a better hospital

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:17.940
Because...

00:11:18.279 --> 00:11:19.700
within six months

00:11:19.759 --> 00:11:22.000
he's going to jail for corruption

00:11:22.220 --> 00:11:23.179
You're slandering me

00:11:25.019 --> 00:11:26.779
So you're that kind of person

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.080
Stay away from me

00:11:31.559 --> 00:11:32.580
Just now

00:11:32.700 --> 00:11:33.980
you said you liked me

00:11:34.539 --> 00:11:35.440
Is that true?

00:11:36.100 --> 00:11:36.779
Of course

00:11:37.600 --> 00:11:38.080
Come

00:11:38.440 --> 00:11:39.139
My dear

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:40.940
Let's go

00:11:44.919 --> 00:11:46.259
This hurdle in life

00:11:46.820 --> 00:11:47.940
has finally been crossed

00:11:49.259 --> 00:11:50.059
Young man

00:11:51.259 --> 00:11:52.500
A beautiful future

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:53.720
belongs to you

00:12:02.860 --> 00:12:03.700
Your dad

00:12:03.879 --> 00:12:04.740
Why doesn't he agree

00:12:04.740 --> 00:12:05.919
to us dating?

00:12:06.139 --> 00:12:07.500
My dad insists on introducing me to

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:08.799
his old comrade's son

00:12:09.019 --> 00:12:10.559
Says you have a weak character

00:12:10.559 --> 00:12:11.500
and no future

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:12.600
What?

00:12:12.940 --> 00:12:13.320
I...

00:12:13.700 --> 00:12:14.879
How am I weak?

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:17.039
With this body of mine

00:12:17.100 --> 00:12:17.480
I...

00:12:21.679 --> 00:12:23.960
That doesn't mean I have no future, right?

00:12:25.519 --> 00:12:26.340
When I meet your dad

00:12:27.259 --> 00:12:29.600
I'll definitely change his opinion of me

00:12:29.919 --> 00:12:31.480
You'd better watch your words

00:12:32.159 --> 00:12:33.679
My dad is ex-military

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:36.480
His temper is a bit explosive

00:12:39.179 --> 00:12:39.879
Your dad

00:12:41.639 --> 00:12:42.440
Is he very fierce?

00:12:42.899 --> 00:12:44.740
He's just very straightforward

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:46.980
Anyway, I've been afraid of him since childhood

00:12:49.879 --> 00:12:50.980
I... well...

00:12:51.519 --> 00:12:52.639
You're so brave

00:12:53.100 --> 00:12:54.440
You wouldn't be afraid of him too, right?

00:12:54.919 --> 00:12:55.860
I...

00:12:56.120 --> 00:12:57.379
Of course I...

00:12:59.019 --> 00:13:00.100
Old Fan

00:13:00.379 --> 00:13:02.120
Stop yelling. Chickened out again?

00:13:03.620 --> 00:13:05.080
He's ex-military

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:06.620
How can I not be nervous?

00:13:07.919 --> 00:13:08.960
I originally thought

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:11.000
a successful confession meant victory

00:13:11.259 --> 00:13:13.059
Who knew I had character flaws

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.879
Life is full of hurdles

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:17.659
By the way

00:13:18.779 --> 00:13:20.200
aren't you a time traveler?

00:13:20.679 --> 00:13:22.860
Tell me some info about this old man

00:13:23.100 --> 00:13:24.840
So I can totally outclass him

00:13:24.919 --> 00:13:25.720
This time

00:13:25.879 --> 00:13:27.100
you can't cheat

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:28.120
Back then

00:13:28.259 --> 00:13:30.179
I never even met this old man

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.580
Don't disappear on me

00:13:32.799 --> 00:13:33.779
What should I do?

00:13:42.220 --> 00:13:42.759
Dad

00:13:43.379 --> 00:13:44.500
This is Dacheng

00:13:50.940 --> 00:13:52.200
Greetings, Father-in-law

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:53.379
Who is your father-in-law?

00:13:54.399 --> 00:13:55.440
You want to marry my daughter?

00:13:56.019 --> 00:13:57.200
Have you passed my test?

00:13:58.659 --> 00:13:59.679
Dad

00:14:00.059 --> 00:14:00.799
What are you doing?

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:01.539
Father-in-law

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:04.039
Sir, please quell your anger and hear me out

00:14:04.519 --> 00:14:05.840
Your humble son-in-law

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:07.279
This humble scholar

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:08.379
Fan Dacheng

00:14:08.960 --> 00:14:10.299
Is truly in love with Ling'ai

00:14:10.299 --> 00:14:10.960
Wait a minute

00:14:12.379 --> 00:14:14.519
Who is this person named Ling'ai?

00:14:16.559 --> 00:14:17.220
See that?

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:18.620
He's seeing someone on the side

00:14:19.019 --> 00:14:19.980
No

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:21.580
Ling'ai just means your daughter

00:14:23.159 --> 00:14:24.600
When did you change your name?

00:14:25.220 --> 00:14:26.000
Dad

00:14:26.039 --> 00:14:27.919
Nay

00:14:28.940 --> 00:14:30.320
Ling'ai means daughter

00:14:30.600 --> 00:14:32.159
Lingzun means father

00:14:32.580 --> 00:14:33.779
Lingtang means...

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:34.679
Enough

00:14:35.820 --> 00:14:37.740
Talking to you intellectuals

00:14:37.740 --> 00:14:38.799
Is really exhausting

00:14:40.259 --> 00:14:41.679
All pretentious and pedantic

00:14:42.580 --> 00:14:44.539
You're too weak to even truss a chicken

00:14:44.639 --> 00:14:46.580
But you're full of deceitful tricks

00:14:46.620 --> 00:14:47.039
I...

00:14:47.039 --> 00:14:47.779
Heartbreaker

00:14:48.159 --> 00:14:48.860
Heartbreaker Cheng

00:14:49.399 --> 00:14:50.240
Tell my dad

00:14:50.419 --> 00:14:51.500
You aren't that kind of person

00:14:55.340 --> 00:14:56.139
Sir

00:14:56.600 --> 00:14:57.460
I...

00:14:57.620 --> 00:14:58.559
Am not that kind of person

00:14:58.559 --> 00:14:59.360
You aren't?

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:02.399
You aren't weak as a chicken?

00:15:03.820 --> 00:15:04.860
Good then

00:15:05.019 --> 00:15:06.639
Let's test that out

00:15:08.159 --> 00:15:08.519
We...

00:15:08.700 --> 00:15:09.720
Let's arm wrestle

00:15:10.019 --> 00:15:11.159
Come on

00:15:11.379 --> 00:15:12.500
Let me weigh

00:15:12.559 --> 00:15:14.139
What you're made of

00:15:14.139 --> 00:15:14.480
Come on

00:15:14.519 --> 00:15:15.399
But I...

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:15.840
I...

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:16.779
Dacheng

00:15:16.940 --> 00:15:17.480
Go for it

00:15:18.019 --> 00:15:19.340
I...

00:15:19.820 --> 00:15:21.500
I'm afraid I can't beat you

00:15:21.879 --> 00:15:23.340
You, a young lad

00:15:23.600 --> 00:15:25.279
Can't beat me, an old man?

00:15:26.580 --> 00:15:28.120
If you can't, that's great

00:15:28.179 --> 00:15:29.820
Then don't marry my precious daughter

00:15:30.519 --> 00:15:31.399
Dacheng

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.779
Go on, do it

00:15:33.519 --> 00:15:34.340
Okay

00:15:34.519 --> 00:15:35.159
I'll do it

00:15:41.019 --> 00:15:41.940
Come, sit tight, sit tight

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:43.919
Here goes

00:15:45.019 --> 00:15:45.740
Go

00:15:56.559 --> 00:15:57.639
You've got some strength

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:08.460
It seems

00:16:09.759 --> 00:16:12.019
I still can't get past this hurdle

00:16:14.340 --> 00:16:15.019
Jing Xian

00:16:16.639 --> 00:16:17.440
I'm sorry

00:16:19.019 --> 00:16:19.759
The two of us

00:16:21.620 --> 00:16:22.740
Let's reconsider

00:16:29.379 --> 00:16:30.960
Can't say I didn't have a chance

00:16:31.879 --> 00:16:33.320
It's just my nature

00:16:34.580 --> 00:16:36.419
It's just my nature

00:16:37.240 --> 00:16:38.720
It's just my nature

00:16:40.039 --> 00:16:42.000
It's just my nature

00:16:46.500 --> 00:16:47.139
Old Fan

00:16:48.600 --> 00:16:49.179
Old Fan

00:16:53.799 --> 00:16:54.720
What are you doing?

00:16:55.399 --> 00:16:57.080
Grinding teeth, sleep-talking, smacking lips

00:16:57.240 --> 00:16:58.779
Burping, farting, having fits

00:16:58.840 --> 00:17:00.320
How am I supposed to share a room with you?

00:17:00.860 --> 00:17:01.659
Nightmare

00:17:02.600 --> 00:17:04.599
I dreamt my first love...

00:17:04.859 --> 00:17:05.799
Married you

00:17:06.319 --> 00:17:07.940
Marrying me is a nightmare?

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:09.059
Actually

00:17:09.819 --> 00:17:10.779
If she married you

00:17:10.839 --> 00:17:12.079
That would be a nightmare for her

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:12.880
Go to sleep

00:17:26.819 --> 00:17:27.519
Little Li

00:17:32.299 --> 00:17:33.019
Who are you?

00:17:34.339 --> 00:17:34.880
Why do you...

00:17:35.660 --> 00:17:36.660
look familiar?

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:39.579
I am you, thirty years from now.

00:17:40.319 --> 00:17:41.279
Thirty years later?

00:17:41.519 --> 00:17:42.440
Did I get rich?

00:17:42.799 --> 00:17:43.900
Did I save up 20,000 yuan?

00:17:44.019 --> 00:17:45.019
Look at you.

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:46.099
Me?

00:17:46.660 --> 00:17:47.779
Look at your ambition.

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:50.400
You could have been the head of the company.

00:17:50.579 --> 00:17:51.779
Managing hundreds of people.

00:17:52.500 --> 00:17:53.900
But because of your bad temper...

00:17:53.900 --> 00:17:54.759
and impulsiveness...

00:17:55.259 --> 00:17:56.019
the deal...

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:59.880
the very deal you're negotiating today...

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:01.079
got blown.

00:18:02.299 --> 00:18:04.299
The boss sent us to manage logistics.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:06.859
We were always sidelined at the company.

00:18:07.099 --> 00:18:09.480
And finally retired in frustration.

00:18:12.940 --> 00:18:14.940
So this deal I'm negotiating today...

00:18:15.759 --> 00:18:16.920
determines my whole life?

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:18.200
What do you think?

00:18:19.900 --> 00:18:21.160
You have to hold your fire.

00:18:21.799 --> 00:18:22.900
Swallow your anger.

00:18:23.660 --> 00:18:24.940
No matter how aggrieved...

00:18:25.299 --> 00:18:27.059
you must close this deal.

00:18:28.279 --> 00:18:29.519
If you close this deal...

00:18:29.519 --> 00:18:32.099
you'll get past this hurdle in life.

00:18:33.039 --> 00:18:33.660
Understand?

00:18:34.900 --> 00:18:36.000
Understood.

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:38.819
You can rest assured.

00:18:40.359 --> 00:18:41.380
I'll rest easy then.

00:18:43.440 --> 00:18:44.099
Um...

00:18:47.579 --> 00:18:48.599
He hung up just like that.

00:18:58.259 --> 00:18:59.079
Manager Wu.

00:18:59.519 --> 00:19:00.380
Manager Wu.

00:19:00.759 --> 00:19:01.619
Sorry, so sorry.

00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:02.519
I'm a little late.

00:19:04.500 --> 00:19:05.480
We agreed on nine o'clock.

00:19:06.200 --> 00:19:07.460
Look what time it is now.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:12.440
Nine o'clock and one minute.

00:19:13.819 --> 00:19:14.720
One minute.

00:19:16.119 --> 00:19:17.700
One minute is still late.

00:19:18.539 --> 00:19:19.759
My one minute...

00:19:20.019 --> 00:19:21.799
is more precious than a whole week of yours, kid.

00:19:21.799 --> 00:19:22.579
Do you know that?

00:19:22.960 --> 00:19:23.579
I...

00:19:23.579 --> 00:19:24.059
Endure.

00:19:24.380 --> 00:19:25.140
Must endure.

00:19:29.539 --> 00:19:30.400
Right.

00:19:30.900 --> 00:19:31.519
Manager Wu.

00:19:32.099 --> 00:19:33.400
A big shot like you...

00:19:33.700 --> 00:19:35.380
must be attending to a myriad of affairs.

00:19:35.420 --> 00:19:36.759
A moment is worth a thousand gold.

00:19:37.339 --> 00:19:38.339
After you...

00:19:38.980 --> 00:19:40.480
I have to meet a few foreign guests.

00:19:41.500 --> 00:19:42.460
At 9:28.

00:19:42.819 --> 00:19:44.160
I'm meeting some French people.

00:19:44.779 --> 00:19:45.960
At 9:58.

00:19:46.420 --> 00:19:47.740
I'm meeting some Germans.

00:19:48.819 --> 00:19:49.880
At 10:28.

00:19:50.059 --> 00:19:51.579
I'm meeting some more French people.

00:19:51.759 --> 00:19:53.440
Manager Wu.

00:19:54.440 --> 00:19:56.859
Let's not talk about the French and Germans.

00:19:57.920 --> 00:19:59.640
Let's talk about our contract.

00:20:00.619 --> 00:20:01.359
Look...

00:20:01.619 --> 00:20:04.099
I've run back and forth several times.

00:20:04.619 --> 00:20:05.480
Today...

00:20:05.700 --> 00:20:07.660
just help us sign this contract.

00:20:07.660 --> 00:20:08.220
Okay?

00:20:08.799 --> 00:20:09.559
What contract?

00:20:14.059 --> 00:20:15.559
Such a tiny little contract

00:20:15.559 --> 00:20:17.019
asking me to sign it personally

00:20:18.500 --> 00:20:19.720
is an insult to me

00:20:21.299 --> 00:20:22.579
For a small contract like yours

00:20:22.680 --> 00:20:24.539
the lame old doorman could sign it

00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:26.440
What lame old... I...

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:27.099
Must endure

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:28.039
Hold it in

00:20:31.700 --> 00:20:32.539
Okay

00:20:33.099 --> 00:20:34.099
I'll endure

00:20:34.559 --> 00:20:35.220
Endure

00:20:38.960 --> 00:20:39.839
Who are you talking to?

00:20:42.339 --> 00:20:43.079
No one

00:20:43.779 --> 00:20:44.880
Let me tell you

00:20:45.779 --> 00:20:48.759
You should thank me for the rest of your life

00:20:49.039 --> 00:20:50.319
for the opportunity I gave you

00:20:50.740 --> 00:20:52.339
You need to be grateful to me forever

00:20:53.180 --> 00:20:54.000
You know that, kid?

00:20:54.220 --> 00:20:56.319
You keep calling me kid this, kid that

00:20:56.319 --> 00:20:56.859
You're just...

00:20:56.859 --> 00:20:58.160
Endure

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:02.940
Right

00:21:03.880 --> 00:21:04.799
I must be grateful

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:06.039
Grateful

00:21:06.519 --> 00:21:07.460
That's better

00:21:07.900 --> 00:21:08.599
I...

00:21:08.980 --> 00:21:10.119
am magnanimous

00:21:10.579 --> 00:21:11.819
and merciful

00:21:12.220 --> 00:21:13.519
Great kindness needs no thanks

00:21:13.519 --> 00:21:14.839
At worst, I just won't sign it

00:21:15.740 --> 00:21:16.460
What did you say?

00:21:17.660 --> 00:21:18.180
Nothing

00:21:18.799 --> 00:21:20.240
Just this bit of small business

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:21.180
I'm just

00:21:21.539 --> 00:21:22.960
treating it like charity for a beggar

00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:24.839
Who are you calling a beggar?

00:21:24.900 --> 00:21:25.420
Endure... I...

00:21:25.420 --> 00:21:26.299
I got it

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:30.960
Manager Wu

00:21:32.380 --> 00:21:33.619
You're a big company

00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:34.859
and we're a small business

00:21:35.640 --> 00:21:37.519
But in a business partnership

00:21:37.519 --> 00:21:39.019
there should be some equality

00:21:39.539 --> 00:21:40.079
E...

00:21:40.299 --> 00:21:41.339
Equality?

00:21:41.940 --> 00:21:42.839
You...

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:45.579
What makes you think you're my equal?

00:21:46.859 --> 00:21:48.220
I'm giving you this business

00:21:48.599 --> 00:21:50.380
I'm giving you this opportunity

00:21:51.079 --> 00:21:52.420
so you have to listen to what I say

00:21:52.420 --> 00:21:53.460
I refuse to listen

00:21:55.200 --> 00:21:56.180
Take all this nonsense

00:21:56.180 --> 00:21:58.140
and go tell it to your French and Germans

00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:01.359
Always calling me "kid" this and "kid" that

00:22:02.059 --> 00:22:02.779
This contract

00:22:03.339 --> 00:22:04.500
I'm not signing it!

00:22:07.539 --> 00:22:08.259
Old Li

00:22:08.559 --> 00:22:09.200
Boss Li

00:22:09.759 --> 00:22:11.259
Me from thirty years later

00:22:12.519 --> 00:22:13.039
It's all my fault

00:22:13.619 --> 00:22:14.960
It's mainly my personality

00:22:14.960 --> 00:22:16.059
Once I start talking, I just...

00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:17.720
Don't I know you?

00:22:18.859 --> 00:22:20.160
My own personality

00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:22.980
It ruins things

00:22:23.519 --> 00:22:25.000
Impulsiveness is the devil

00:22:25.119 --> 00:22:25.960
Okay

00:22:26.279 --> 00:22:26.880
I'll change

00:22:27.339 --> 00:22:28.819
I'll change, alright?

00:22:28.920 --> 00:22:29.740
Change?

00:22:30.299 --> 00:22:31.299
You'll never

00:22:33.539 --> 00:22:34.460
I'll never

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:36.420
be able to change

00:22:38.619 --> 00:22:39.759
Go explain it to the Chairman

00:22:40.180 --> 00:22:40.720
Remember

00:22:41.259 --> 00:22:43.079
don't let him transfer you to logistics

00:22:43.900 --> 00:22:44.779
Got it

00:22:45.500 --> 00:22:47.359
Don't get exiled to logistics

00:22:49.519 --> 00:22:50.319
Hung up again

00:22:52.559 --> 00:22:54.059
So I'll have this temper even when I'm old

00:23:04.220 --> 00:23:04.960
Manager Jia

00:23:06.819 --> 00:23:07.680
Manager Jia

00:23:11.900 --> 00:23:14.019
It was just a moment of impulse

00:23:15.660 --> 00:23:17.539
Your personal impulse

00:23:17.759 --> 00:23:19.079
How can we stand it?

00:23:19.819 --> 00:23:21.579
The company is losing money and collapsing

00:23:22.019 --> 00:23:23.759
This was our lifeline

00:23:23.859 --> 00:23:24.380
Yes

00:23:24.380 --> 00:23:26.039
We were just about to sign the contract

00:23:26.259 --> 00:23:27.160
But look at you

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:28.980
You scared Manager Wu away

00:23:31.380 --> 00:23:33.420
I have to say, Manager Jia, you are talented

00:23:33.980 --> 00:23:35.299
Even your scolding rhymes

00:23:36.839 --> 00:23:38.319
Were you a poet in the past?

00:23:39.740 --> 00:23:40.440
Don't interrupt

00:23:41.279 --> 00:23:42.339
From today on

00:23:43.539 --> 00:23:45.859
stop messing around in the Marketing Department

00:23:46.279 --> 00:23:47.319
Go to the Logistics Department

00:23:47.740 --> 00:23:49.660
and help with the cleaning

00:23:49.660 --> 00:23:50.660
Don't

00:23:51.059 --> 00:23:52.680
Please don't, Manager Jia

00:23:53.660 --> 00:23:54.640
I beg you

00:23:55.059 --> 00:23:57.460
Please don't banish me to Logistics

00:23:58.519 --> 00:23:59.380
I'll change this temper

00:23:59.819 --> 00:24:00.700
I promise you

00:24:01.059 --> 00:24:03.400
I will definitely sign a big deal for our company

00:24:04.460 --> 00:24:05.579
Change your temper?

00:24:06.940 --> 00:24:08.279
My experience is...

00:24:09.079 --> 00:24:10.319
The seas may dry

00:24:10.380 --> 00:24:11.519
mountains may fall

00:24:11.619 --> 00:24:13.640
but a temper can never be changed

00:24:14.119 --> 00:24:15.119
If you want to change careers

00:24:15.140 --> 00:24:16.359
you'd better do it early

00:24:16.579 --> 00:24:18.539
Or you'll regret it in old age when no one wants you

00:24:19.299 --> 00:24:20.920
As for your job as Marketing Director

00:24:21.660 --> 00:24:23.200
I've already assigned it to Xiao Ma

00:24:26.339 --> 00:24:27.099
Which Xiao Ma?

00:24:28.839 --> 00:24:29.740
The new guy

00:24:30.380 --> 00:24:31.619
The one chasing your daughter all day?

00:24:31.880 --> 00:24:32.660
That's right

00:24:33.259 --> 00:24:34.180
Last month

00:24:34.180 --> 00:24:35.380
he and my daughter

00:24:36.180 --> 00:24:37.240
got married

00:24:38.460 --> 00:24:39.440
I see

00:24:40.180 --> 00:24:42.460
He's the one badmouthing me to you all day

00:24:43.140 --> 00:24:43.640
No

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:46.180
As a leader

00:24:46.420 --> 00:24:47.539
you shouldn't practice nepotism

00:24:47.539 --> 00:24:48.599
and suppress a key contributor

00:24:50.319 --> 00:24:51.920
Are you here to admit your mistake

00:24:51.940 --> 00:24:52.859
or

00:24:53.079 --> 00:24:54.380
or are you here to be insubordinate?

00:24:54.460 --> 00:24:55.880
I'm just stating the facts

00:24:56.480 --> 00:24:58.460
I knew long ago you were pushing me out

00:24:58.839 --> 00:24:59.880
If you don't need me, fine

00:25:00.319 --> 00:25:02.099
I'm quitting!

00:25:02.200 --> 00:25:03.339
I'm done serving you

00:25:03.900 --> 00:25:05.640
Darn it

00:25:05.839 --> 00:25:06.700
That bad temper of his

00:25:07.460 --> 00:25:08.279
This bad temper of mine

00:25:08.279 --> 00:25:10.000
Why can't he change it?

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:11.299
It ruins things

00:25:19.019 --> 00:25:20.460
It seems after all these years

00:25:21.160 --> 00:25:23.380
my personality has changed a bit

00:25:26.700 --> 00:25:28.519
Impulse is the devil

00:25:29.319 --> 00:25:30.039
Impulse

00:25:30.420 --> 00:25:31.180
is the devil

00:25:32.680 --> 00:25:33.980
Impulse is the devil

00:25:37.940 --> 00:25:38.940
Where is the devil?

00:25:40.559 --> 00:25:41.299
Impulse

00:25:44.180 --> 00:25:44.940
Impulse

00:25:48.440 --> 00:25:50.180
Impulse is the devil

00:25:50.740 --> 00:25:52.180
What is this nonsense?

00:25:52.779 --> 00:25:54.039
Did you have a nightmare too?

00:25:54.619 --> 00:25:55.240
Go to sleep

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:05.380
Straight.

00:26:07.019 --> 00:26:07.559
Pass.

00:26:08.400 --> 00:26:09.180
8 to Queen.

00:26:11.559 --> 00:26:12.359
So,

00:26:12.539 --> 00:26:14.299
the dreams you two had last night

00:26:14.359 --> 00:26:15.819
were like a TV series.

00:26:17.319 --> 00:26:18.259
Crystal clear.

00:26:18.440 --> 00:26:20.079
I had a dream last night too.

00:26:21.000 --> 00:26:22.180
I dreamt that I...

00:26:22.720 --> 00:26:23.759
encountered that...

00:26:23.759 --> 00:26:25.539
opportunity from my youth again.

00:26:25.759 --> 00:26:26.559
Did you act in it this time?

00:26:26.559 --> 00:26:27.599
Did you run into Director Zhang again?

00:26:27.779 --> 00:26:28.579
I did.

00:26:28.920 --> 00:26:29.859
Became a big star.

00:26:30.279 --> 00:26:31.099
It was okay.

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:34.259
But with my personality...

00:26:34.400 --> 00:26:35.180
Social anxiety.

00:26:35.759 --> 00:26:37.160
I didn't get along with the director,

00:26:37.380 --> 00:26:38.460
and didn't know how to socialize.

00:26:39.700 --> 00:26:40.579
In the end,

00:26:41.599 --> 00:26:42.599
I went back to the Children's Art Theatre.

00:26:46.339 --> 00:26:47.500
To tell you the truth,

00:26:47.759 --> 00:26:49.380
I had a dream last night too.

00:26:50.180 --> 00:26:52.779
I dreamt of that handsome guy from back then.

00:26:54.619 --> 00:26:56.519
Did you dream you married the Chief Engineer

00:26:56.519 --> 00:26:58.119
and lived happily ever after?

00:26:59.619 --> 00:27:01.180
Happy my foot.

00:27:02.019 --> 00:27:03.559
I dreamt that man

00:27:03.559 --> 00:27:05.160
still died early of illness.

00:27:05.519 --> 00:27:07.920
And I still raised the child alone.

00:27:08.539 --> 00:27:10.519
With a useless son and a wicked daughter-in-law.

00:27:10.740 --> 00:27:12.039
Xiao Cai, you're a husband-killer.

00:27:12.039 --> 00:27:12.720
Pah.

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:13.960
Does it count in a dream?

00:27:14.299 --> 00:27:15.119
Superstitious nonsense.

00:27:15.319 --> 00:27:16.079
Exactly.

00:27:16.240 --> 00:27:17.880
My fate is in my own hands.

00:27:19.140 --> 00:27:19.880
It's destiny.

00:27:20.299 --> 00:27:21.559
It is superstition, true.

00:27:21.619 --> 00:27:22.619
But a person's character,

00:27:22.619 --> 00:27:23.779
to a large extent,

00:27:23.880 --> 00:27:25.160
determines their destiny.

00:27:25.519 --> 00:27:26.799
Actually, life...

00:27:27.220 --> 00:27:28.019
is not about

00:27:28.420 --> 00:27:29.299
fate determined by opportunity,

00:27:29.359 --> 00:27:30.400
but fate determined by character.

00:27:30.559 --> 00:27:31.720
Well said.

00:27:31.960 --> 00:27:32.940
What do you mean?

00:27:34.440 --> 00:27:36.779
People often attribute failure and unhappiness

00:27:36.980 --> 00:27:38.480
to not having good opportunities,

00:27:38.599 --> 00:27:39.279
or

00:27:40.099 --> 00:27:41.279
missing out on good opportunities.

00:27:42.079 --> 00:27:43.279
Opportunities are certainly important,

00:27:43.980 --> 00:27:45.920
but if your character is like that,

00:27:46.079 --> 00:27:47.380
no matter what opportunity you encounter,

00:27:47.559 --> 00:27:48.660
the result will be the same.

00:27:50.539 --> 00:27:51.700
Now that you mention it,

00:27:51.900 --> 00:27:52.759
I still don't get it.

00:27:54.059 --> 00:27:55.519
Professor Fan means that

00:27:55.599 --> 00:27:57.940
opportunity favors the prepared.

00:27:59.339 --> 00:28:00.220
Four. Who covers?

00:28:01.420 --> 00:28:01.940
Six.

00:28:03.039 --> 00:28:03.539
Red Joker.

00:28:06.140 --> 00:28:07.099
After saying all that,

00:28:07.819 --> 00:28:08.440
the most important thing,

00:28:08.440 --> 00:28:09.359
you still haven't said.

00:28:10.220 --> 00:28:11.059
What thing?

00:28:12.660 --> 00:28:14.079
Are you still going abroad?

00:28:15.460 --> 00:28:17.700
Listening to the elders' stories these past two days,

00:28:17.799 --> 00:28:18.920
I feel that

00:28:19.000 --> 00:28:20.259
I need to change my personality.

00:28:20.539 --> 00:28:22.420
I need to see what suits me better,

00:28:22.500 --> 00:28:24.099
and work towards it,

00:28:24.099 --> 00:28:24.819
so I have no regrets.

00:28:26.819 --> 00:28:28.259
So you're still going abroad then?

00:28:28.539 --> 00:28:29.400
So,

00:28:29.799 --> 00:28:30.740
I've decided,

00:28:30.819 --> 00:28:31.500
not to go abroad.

00:28:32.099 --> 00:28:33.220
I knew it.

00:28:36.359 --> 00:28:37.019
What did you say?

00:28:37.759 --> 00:28:39.960
I've always been my parents' good girl.

00:28:40.019 --> 00:28:41.380
I never had my own mind.

00:28:41.799 --> 00:28:42.980
That's a problem with my personality.

00:28:43.059 --> 00:28:43.700
I want to

00:28:43.799 --> 00:28:44.500
change.

00:28:46.079 --> 00:28:46.539
Right.

00:28:47.480 --> 00:28:48.259
Our destiny,

00:28:49.059 --> 00:28:49.779
we decide.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:07.519
My mom.

00:29:09.579 --> 00:29:10.200
Hello?

00:29:10.460 --> 00:29:11.259
Mommy.

00:29:12.460 --> 00:29:13.359
I've decided

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.180
not to go abroad.

00:29:15.539 --> 00:29:17.960
I know you mean well.

00:29:21.619 --> 00:29:23.059
Changed to Harvard again?

00:29:25.059 --> 00:29:26.960
That's too complicated.

00:29:27.319 --> 00:29:27.740
No,

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:28.660
I...

00:29:28.900 --> 00:29:30.279
You have a point.

00:29:30.680 --> 00:29:31.220
Right.